.class public auto ansi sealed beforefieldinit Ikev2VpnProfile extends Android.Net.PlatformVpnProfile

Docs.summary: The Ikev2VpnProfile is a configuration for the platform setup of IKEv2/IPsec VPNs.

remarks.para: The Ikev2VpnProfile is a configuration for the platform setup of IKEv2/IPsec VPNs.
Together with VpnManager, this allows apps to provision IKEv2/IPsec VPNs that do not require the VPN app to constantly run in the background.
